		{
			"name": "Webhooks (Sprint 4)",
			"description": "Webhook Receiver Pattern (`POST /api/v1/webhooks/{provider}/{event}`) com HMAC-SHA256 + `Idempotency-Key` + Outbox stub. Preparação para Epic 15 (Pix) e Epic 5 (KYC callbacks Celcoin).\n\n**Headers obrigatórios:**\n- `Idempotency-Key`: UUID/string única por evento\n- `X-Webhook-Signature`: hex lowercase do HMAC-SHA256(secret, payload)\n\n**Como gerar a assinatura no Postman (Pre-request Script):**\n```js\nconst secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('webhookSecret');\nconst body = pm.request.body.raw;\nconst hmac = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString();\npm.request.headers.upsert({key: 'X-Webhook-Signature', value: hmac});\n```",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "POST /webhooks/celcoin/pix-recebimento — 202",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "prerequest",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"const secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('webhookSecret');",
									"const body = pm.request.body.raw;",
									"const hmac = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString();",
									"pm.request.headers.upsert({key: 'X-Webhook-Signature', value: hmac});",
									"console.log('signature:', hmac);"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Idempotency-Key",
								"value": "evt-{{$timestamp}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"transactionId\": \"abc-123\",\n  \"valor\": 1500.50,\n  \"chavePix\": \"00000000000\",\n  \"status\": \"LIQUIDADO\"\n}"
